     H            Y.
     F** AAVR10 **********************************************
     F* ASJ HALF PRODUCT KANBAN # UPDATE BASED ON THE IAF PART#.       .
     F* THIS IS CALLED FROM AAVR01.
     F*   TCH      FEB/15/02
     F*
     F********************************************** AAVR10 **
     FFCEPL40 IF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL01 UF  E           K        DISK
     FFCEPL11 UF  E           K        DISK
     FAAUPL01 UF  E           K        DISK
     FGHCPL21 UF  E           K        DISK
     FAAMPL11 UF  E           K        DISK
     FAAPPL03 UF  E           K        DISK
      *------------------------------------------------------
     E                    FKH        10  8 0             UPDATE DATE
     E                    FKM        10 10               UPDATE TIME
     E                    FGK        10  9 0             MONTHLY QTY
     E                    FGH        10  8 0             CHANGE DATE
     E                    FCD        10  3 1             WORK DAYS
      *------------------------------------------------------
     I            DS
     I                                        1  800FKH
     I                                        1   80FCKH01
