     I                                       46  540FCGK06
     I                                       55  630FCGK07
     I                                       64  720FCGK08
     I                                       73  810FCGK09
     I                                       82  900FCGK10
     I            DS
     I                                        1  800FGH
     I                                        1   80FCGH01
